rings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6651 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/24\/plant-trees-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20983,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Plant your trees in Paradise with remembrance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your plantings in Paradise, for its water is sweet and its soil is clean. Its plantings are to say: there is no movement or might but in Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 13354 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/22\/their-only-regret-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20983,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Their only regret is not remembering Allah more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people of Paradise will have no regrets, except for moments that passed by them in which they did not remember Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam